    <stitle>INTERNATIONAL&#174; VT 365 DIESEL ENGINE - FUEL SYSTEM - Installation - Fuel Filter Assembly and Tubing
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="4">
        <title>Fuel Filter Assembly and Tubing</title>
        <figure id="f2351211" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd11/d1104.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 447. Installing fuel filter assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install fuel filter assembly onto intake manifold. Secure assembly with two M10 x 20
                mounting bolts. Tighten bolts to the standard torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect filter water drain tubing.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2351209" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd11/d1119.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 448. Fuel supply and return O-rings</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel return O-ring</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel supply O-ring</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Replace all O-rings at fuel return and supply fittings. Replace all banjo fitting copper
                washers at cylinder heads.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2351212" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd11/d1102.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 449. Filter drain and cylinder head fuel supply tubing</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Water drain tube assembly</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Filter to left cylinder head tube assembly</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Filter to right cylinder head tube assembly</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect fuel tubing fittings to fuel filter assembly and leave hand tight. Connect banjo
                fitting ends to the left and right cylinder heads. Anchor right side fuel tubing to EGR cooler stud.
                Tighten all fittings to the special torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2351213" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd11/d1105.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 450. Connecting fuel supply and return tubing</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel return tube assembly</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel supply tube assembly</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect chassis fuel supply and return tube assembly to fuel filter assembly and tighten
                fittings to the special torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Fuel filter drain lever must be closed.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
